CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Jiuzi Holdings Inc operates as a franchise under the brand name Jiuzi. It sells new energy vehicles in third-fourth tier cities in China. The firm also sells plug-in electric vehicles on-demand from vehicle buyers. Its business segments are sales of NEVs and franchise services. The company generates a majority of its revenue from franchisee's service. Geographically, the firm operates in China.
